---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="The Contract | Blackbox" currentPage="contract">

        <!-- Hero Section -->
        <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center mt-8 mb-20 fade-up">
            <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-white/60 mb-6">
                The Contract
            </h1>
            <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-zinc-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
                The Asana ticket template is the bridge between worlds. Product Owners fill it, Developers consume it.
            </p>
        </section>

        <!-- Why a Contract Callout -->
        <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 mb-24 fade-up delay-100">
            <div class="p-8 md:p-10 rounded-2xl bg-blue-500/5 border border-blue-500/20 text-center relative overflow-hidden">
                <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-64 h-64 bg-blue-500/10 blur-[60px] pointer-events-none"></div>
                <iconify-icon icon="solar:link-circle-linear" class="text-4xl text-blue-400 mb-4"></iconify-icon>
                <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                    Unspecified details create ambiguity. Ambiguity creates inconsistency. The ticket template forces explicit decisions — current behavior, desired behavior, testable requirements. <span class="text-white font-medium">The more specific the ticket, the better the blueprint, the better the code.</span>
                </p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- The Template Tour -->
        <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 mb-32 fade-up">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-12">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-white">The Template</h2>
                <div class="h-px bg-white/10 flex-grow"></div>
            </div>

            <div class="space-y-8">

                <!-- Goal -->
                <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl border border-blue-500/20 bg-blue-900/5 relative overflow-hidden group hover:border-blue-500/30 transition-colors">
                    <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-blue-500/10 border border-blue-500/20 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
                            <iconify-icon icon="solar:target-linear" class="text-2xl text-blue-400"></iconify-icon>
                        </div>
                        <div class="w-full">
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-white mb-2">Goal</h3>
                            <p class="text-base text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed mb-6">
                                What are we building and why? One clear sentence. If you can't say it in one sentence, the scope is too big — split the ticket.
                            </p>
                            <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                                <div class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-red-500/5 border border-red-500/20">
                                    <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
                                        <iconify-icon icon="solar:close-circle-linear" class="text-red-400"></iconify-icon>
                                        <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-red-400 uppercase tracking-wider">Bad Example</span>
                                    </div>
                                    <p class="text-sm text-zinc-300">"Improve the dashboard"</p>
                                </div>
                                <div class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-emerald-500/5 border border-emerald-500/20">
                                    <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
                                        <iconify-icon icon="solar:check-circle-linear" class="text-emerald-400"></iconify-icon>
                                        <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-emerald-400 uppercase tracking-wider">Good Example</span>
                                    </div>
                                    <p class="text-sm text-zinc-300">"Add a date range filter to the orders dashboard so managers can view sales by period"</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Context -->
                <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-zinc-900/20">
                    <div class="flex items-start gap-4 mb-8">
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-zinc-800 border border-zinc-700 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
                            <iconify-icon icon="solar:info-square-linear" class="text-2xl text-zinc-300"></iconify-icon>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-white mb-2">Context</h3>
                            <p class="text-base text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed mb-6">
                                <strong class="text-zinc-300 font-medium">Background:</strong> Why does this matter? What triggered this work?
                            </p>

                            <div class="space-y-6">
                                <!-- Current Behavior -->
                                <div>
                                    <p class="text-sm font-medium text-white mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
                                        <iconify-icon icon="solar:history-linear" class="text-zinc-400"></iconify-icon> Current Behavior
                                    </p>
                                    <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400 mb-3">How does the system work today? Be specific — reference pages, buttons, API endpoints, error messages.</p>
                                    <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                                        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-red-500/5 border border-red-500/20">
                                            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
                                                <iconify-icon icon="solar:close-circle-linear" class="text-red-400"></iconify-icon>
                                                <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-red-400 uppercase tracking-wider">Bad Example</span>
                                            </div>
                                            <p class="text-sm text-zinc-300">"It's slow"</p>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-emerald-500/5 border border-emerald-500/20">
                                            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
                                                <iconify-icon icon="solar:check-circle-linear" class="text-emerald-400"></iconify-icon>
                                                <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-emerald-400 uppercase tracking-wider">Good Example</span>
                                            </div>
                                            <p class="text-sm text-zinc-300">"The orders page takes 8 seconds to load when filtering by date range with more than 10,000 orders"</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>

                                <!-- Desired Behavior -->
                                <div>
                                    <p class="text-sm font-medium text-white mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
                                        <iconify-icon icon="solar:magic-stick-3-linear" class="text-zinc-400"></iconify-icon> Desired Behavior
                                    </p>
                                    <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400 mb-3">Same specificity. Define exactly what should happen.</p>
                                    <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                                        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-red-500/5 border border-red-500/20">
                                            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
                                                <iconify-icon icon="solar:close-circle-linear" class="text-red-400"></iconify-icon>
                                                <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-red-400 uppercase tracking-wider">Bad Example</span>
                                            </div>
                                            <p class="text-sm text-zinc-300">"Make it faster"</p>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-emerald-500/5 border border-emerald-500/20">
                                            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
                                                <iconify-icon icon="solar:check-circle-linear" class="text-emerald-400"></iconify-icon>
                                                <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-emerald-400 uppercase tracking-wider">Good Example</span>
                                            </div>
                                            <p class="text-sm text-zinc-300">"The orders page should load in under 2 seconds regardless of filter or order count"</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Requirements -->
                <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-zinc-900/20">
                    <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-zinc-800 border border-zinc-700 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
                            <iconify-icon icon="solar:checklist-minimalistic-linear" class="text-2xl text-zinc-300"></iconify-icon>
                        </div>
                        <div class="w-full">
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-white mb-2">Requirements</h3>
                            <p class="text-base text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed mb-6">
                                Testable acceptance criteria. Each one must be verifiable — someone should be able to definitively say "yes, this works" or "no, it doesn't."
                            </p>

                            <div class="space-y-3 mb-6">
                                <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-3 rounded-lg bg-[#0d0d12] border border-red-500/20">
                                    <iconify-icon icon="solar:close-square-linear" class="text-red-400 text-lg mt-0.5"></iconify-icon>
                                    <span class="text-sm text-zinc-400 line-through">improve performance</span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-3 rounded-lg bg-[#0d0d12] border border-emerald-500/20">
                                    <iconify-icon icon="solar:check-square-linear" class="text-emerald-400 text-lg mt-0.5"></iconify-icon>
                                    <span class="text-sm text-zinc-300">page loads in under 2 seconds on 3G</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- UI / UX -->
                <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl border border-purple-500/20 bg-purple-900/5 relative overflow-hidden group hover:border-purple-500/30 transition-colors">
                    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-purple-500/10 blur-[50px] pointer-events-none"></div>
                    <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-purple-500/10 border border-purple-500/20 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
                            <iconify-icon icon="solar:pen-new-square-linear" class="text-2xl text-purple-400"></iconify-icon>
                        </div>
                        <div class="w-full">
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-white mb-2">UI / UX</h3>
                            <p class="text-base text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed mb-6">
                                Filled by the Designer when the ticket goes through the design phase. Covers screens/flows, component choices (referencing existing components by name), and mockup attachments. Marked <span class="font-mono text-sm text-zinc-300">N/A</span> if no design needed.
                            </p>
                            <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                                <div class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-red-500/5 border border-red-500/20">
                                    <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
                                        <iconify-icon icon="solar:close-circle-linear" class="text-red-400"></iconify-icon>
                                        <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-red-400 uppercase tracking-wider">Bad Example</span>
                                    </div>
                                    <p class="text-sm text-zinc-300">"Make it look nice, maybe a modal"</p>
                                </div>
                                <div class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-emerald-500/5 border border-emerald-500/20">
                                    <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
                                        <iconify-icon icon="solar:check-circle-linear" class="text-emerald-400"></iconify-icon>
                                        <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-emerald-400 uppercase tracking-wider">Good Example</span>
                                    </div>
                                    <p class="text-sm text-zinc-300">"Use the existing DateRangePicker component. Filter appears inline above the table, same layout as the reports page. See attached mockup."</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Constraints -->
                <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-zinc-900/20">
                    <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-zinc-800 border border-zinc-700 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
                            <iconify-icon icon="solar:shield-warning-linear" class="text-2xl text-zinc-300"></iconify-icon>
                        </div>
                        <div class="w-full">
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-white mb-2">Constraints</h3>
                            <p class="text-base text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed mb-6">
                                Non-negotiable rules. Performance budgets, browser support, backwards compatibility, security requirements.
                            </p>
                            <div class="space-y-3">
                                <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-3 rounded-lg bg-[#0d0d12] border border-zinc-700/50">
                                    <iconify-icon icon="solar:shield-warning-linear" class="text-amber-400 text-lg mt-0.5"></iconify-icon>
                                    <span class="text-sm text-zinc-300">Must not break existing API contracts — all v1 endpoints remain unchanged</span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-3 rounded-lg bg-[#0d0d12] border border-zinc-700/50">
                                    <iconify-icon icon="solar:shield-warning-linear" class="text-amber-400 text-lg mt-0.5"></iconify-icon>
                                    <span class="text-sm text-zinc-300">Page must load under 2s on 3G with 10k+ rows</span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-3 rounded-lg bg-[#0d0d12] border border-zinc-700/50">
                                    <iconify-icon icon="solar:shield-warning-linear" class="text-amber-400 text-lg mt-0.5"></iconify-icon>
                                    <span class="text-sm text-zinc-300">No new dependencies — use existing date-fns library</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Open Questions -->
                <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl border border-red-500/20 bg-red-900/5 relative overflow-hidden group hover:border-red-500/30 transition-colors">
                    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-red-500/10 blur-[50px] pointer-events-none"></div>
                    <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-red-500/10 border border-red-500/20 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
                            <iconify-icon icon="solar:question-circle-linear" class="text-2xl text-red-400"></iconify-icon>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-white mb-2">Open Questions</h3>
                            <p class="text-base text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed">
                                Anything unresolved. This section <strong class="text-red-400 font-medium">MUST</strong> be empty before the ticket can move to Ready for Development. This is the hard gate.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Custom Fields & Quality Gates -->
        <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 mb-32 grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 fade-up delay-100">

            <!-- Custom Fields -->
            <div class="lg:col-span-5">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-white mb-6">Custom Fields</h2>
                <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-[#0d0d12] overflow-hidden">
                    <div class="divide-y divide-white/5">
                        <div class="p-4 flex items-center justify-between">
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                                <iconify-icon icon="solar:tag-horizontal-linear" class="text-zinc-400 text-lg"></iconify-icon>
                                <span class="text-sm font-medium text-white">Type</span>
                            </div>
                            <span class="text-xs font-mono text-zinc-400 bg-white/5 px-2 py-1 rounded">feat | fix | improve | hotfix</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="p-4 flex items-center justify-between">
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                                <iconify-icon icon="solar:siren-rounded-linear" class="text-zinc-400 text-lg"></iconify-icon>
                                <span class="text-sm font-medium text-white">Priority</span>
                            </div>
                            <span class="text-xs font-mono text-zinc-400 bg-white/5 px-2 py-1 rounded">Low | Medium | High | Critical</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="p-4">
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
                                <iconify-icon icon="solar:chart-square-linear" class="text-zinc-400 text-lg"></iconify-icon>
                                <span class="text-sm font-medium text-white">Status</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5">
                                <span class="text-[10px] font-mono text-zinc-500 bg-white/5 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded">Draft</span>
                                <span class="text-[10px] font-mono text-zinc-500 bg-white/5 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded">Refining</span>
                                <span class="text-[10px] font-mono text-zinc-500 bg-white/5 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded">Ready for Design</span>
                                <span class="text-[10px] font-mono text-purple-400/70 bg-purple-500/10 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded">Designing</span>
                                <span class="text-[10px] font-mono text-zinc-500 bg-white/5 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded">Ready for Dev</span>
                                <span class="text-[10px] font-mono text-blue-400/70 bg-blue-500/10 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded">In Progress</span>
                                <span class="text-[10px] font-mono text-blue-400/70 bg-blue-500/10 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded">PR Review</span>
                                <span class="text-[10px] font-mono text-blue-400/70 bg-blue-500/10 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded">Ready to Test</span>
                                <span class="text-[10px] font-mono text-emerald-400/70 bg-emerald-500/10 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded">Testing</span>
                                <span class="text-[10px] font-mono text-emerald-400/70 bg-emerald-500/10 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded">Done</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Quality Gates -->
            <div class="lg:col-span-7">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-white mb-6">Quality Gates</h2>
                <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                    <!-- Soft Gate -->
                    <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-amber-500/20 bg-amber-900/5 relative overflow-hidden">
                        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-24 h-24 bg-amber-500/10 blur-[40px] pointer-events-none"></div>
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight text-white mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
                            <iconify-icon icon="solar:shield-warning-linear" class="text-amber-400"></iconify-icon>
                            At Creation
                        </h3>
                        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed mb-4">
                            Claude warns about missing or weak sections but still creates the ticket.
                        </p>
                        <span class="inline-flex items-center px-2 py-1 rounded-md bg-amber-500/10 text-amber-400 text-xs font-medium border border-amber-500/20">Soft Gate</span>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Hard Gate -->
                    <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-red-500/20 bg-red-900/5 relative overflow-hidden">
                        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-24 h-24 bg-red-500/10 blur-[40px] pointer-events-none"></div>
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight text-white mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
                            <iconify-icon icon="solar:lock-password-linear" class="text-red-400"></iconify-icon>
                            At Transition
                        </h3>
                        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed mb-4">
                            Claude blocks moving to <span class="text-zinc-300">Ready for Design/Developer</span> if: Open Questions is not empty, Goal/Requirements are missing, or Behavior is vague.
                        </p>
                        <span class="inline-flex items-center px-2 py-1 rounded-md bg-red-500/10 text-red-400 text-xs font-medium border border-red-500/20">Hard Gate</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

        </section>

        <!-- Role Usage Grid -->
        <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 mb-32 fade-up">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-white mb-8">How Each Role Uses <span class="font-mono text-blue-400">CLAUDE</span></h2>

            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
                <!-- PO -->
                <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-zinc-900/20 flex flex-col">
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
                        <iconify-icon icon="solar:user-linear" class="text-2xl text-orange-400"></iconify-icon>
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight text-white">Product Owners</h3>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed">
                        Fills the template. References actual code for specificity (read-only codebase access). Blocks transitions when quality gates aren't met.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <!-- DESIGN -->
                <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-zinc-900/20 flex flex-col">
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
                        <iconify-icon icon="solar:pallete-2-linear" class="text-2xl text-purple-400"></iconify-icon>
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight text-white">Designers</h3>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed">
                        Fills the UI/UX section. References existing components by name from the codebase. Attaches mockups. Sends back to PO if requirements are unclear.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <!-- DEV -->
                <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-zinc-900/20 flex flex-col">
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
                        <iconify-icon icon="solar:programming-linear" class="text-2xl text-emerald-400"></iconify-icon>
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight text-white flex items-center gap-2">
                            Developers
                            <span class="text-xs font-mono font-normal text-zinc-500 bg-white/5 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded border border-white/10">/scaffold</span>
                        </h3>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed">
                        Parses the template to generate a blueprint. Maps Goal → Blueprint Goal, Context → Blueprint Context, etc. Flags weak sections — developer can proceed or <span class="font-mono text-xs text-zinc-300">/send-back</span>.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- The Bottom Line -->
        <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 mb-16 fade-up">
            <div class="p-8 md:p-12 rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-gradient-to-b from-zinc-900/40 to-transparent text-center relative overflow-hidden">
                <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-64 h-64 bg-blue-500/5 blur-[80px] pointer-events-none"></div>
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-white mb-6">The Contract is a Promise</h2>
                <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-8">
                    When the ticket is complete, every role has done their part. The Product Owner defined the problem. The Designer shaped the experience. The Developer knows exactly what to build. No guessing, no assumptions, no back-and-forth.
                </p>
                <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                    <div class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/5">
                        <p class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-1">Clear input</p>
                        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-500">produces clear output</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/5">
                        <p class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-1">One ticket</p>
                        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-500">one blueprint, one PR</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/5">
                        <p class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-1">Zero ambiguity</p>
                        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-500">at the point of build</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

</BaseLayout>
